</div>
<div class=" row z">
	<p class="typical"> <%= "Affiliated started out as an idea by Armon Battle while he was part of the baseball community in Chapman University. He along with his co-founders saw the parallels between their idea of 'family' in the team to the one held by people in Greek life. With that, he saw how countless amounts of students want to be part of something bigger themselves which henced inspired him to start a company that heavily dedicates itself to helping people get there. In this particular context, through helping Greek life. The company eventually partnered with Chapman's User Experience Society to provide the technical expertise for the project." %>
	</p>	
</div>
<div class="row">
	<h3 class="big head"><%= "The Why" %> </h3> 
</div>
<div class="row y">
			<%= image_tag("affiliated-2-07.png", class: "erd-img" , style:"width:100% !important;") %>
</div>
<div class=" row z">
	<p class="typical"><%= "After the founders conducted extensive reviews, Affiliated sought to solve problems in a two-fold manner. It hopes to provide a way for Greek life members to still feel connected to their brotherhood/sisterhood even after graduation instead of feeling the abrupt end of their life in their respective fraternity or sorority. Moreover, Affiliated hopes to makes the asset management for the people running these organizations variably easier knowing that there are a lot and that it could be too complex to process efficiently for the average college student." %>
</div>
<div class="row">
