</div>
<div class=" row ">
	<p class="typical"><%= " After having a clear understanding of the goal that Affiliated wanted to achieve, we set out in talking and profiling the people involved in Greek Life. From this effort, we managed to get 6 personae (potential members/pledges, executive board, active members, alumni, uniersity admin). Due to a non-disclosure agreement, we're only allowed to show one of the personae: Ellie Briar, the executive board member." %>
	</p>
</div>

<div class="row">
