	</p>
	<br>
</div>
<div class="row y">
			<%= image_tag("affiliated-2-02.png", class: "erd-img") %>
</div>
<div class=" row z">
	<p class="typical"><%= "After that, the whole team got together to whiteboard the whole process of interacting with the application. We critiqued our decisions based on a heuristic guideline and agreed on a user flow" %>
	</p>
	<br>
</div>
<br>
<div class="row y">
			<%= image_tag("affiliated-2-04.png", class: "wired-img") %>
</div>
<br>
<div class=" row z">
	<p class="typical"><%= "Afterwards, we revisted our work as we went about computerizing the overall flow into a design artifact that can be easily understood." %>
	</p>
	<br>
</div>
<div class="row y">
			<%= image_tag("affiliated-2-03.png", class: "wired-img") %>
</div>
<div class=" row z">
